## é¢„æœŸ Attempt æ•°æ®æ ¼å¼ / Expected Attempt Data Format

```json
[
  {
    "attempt": 1,
    "status": "FAILED",
    "duration": 0.5,
    "error": "AssertionError: ...",
    "url": "https://example.com",
    "has_video": true,
    "has_trace": true
  },
  {
    "attempt": 2,
    "status": "PASSED",
    "duration": 0.3
  }
]
```

